export let __workshopId = '2452831710';
'use strict';export var scriptProperties=createScriptProperties().addCombo({name:'language',label:'Language',options:[{label:'English',value:'en-US'},{label:'繁體中文',value:'zh-TW'},{label:'日本語',value:'ja-JP'}]}).addCombo({name:'week',label:'Weekday Type',options:[{label:'Narrow (e.g. T)',value:'narrow'},{label:'Short (e.g. Thu)',value:'short'},{label:'Long (e.g. Thursday)',value:'long'}]}).addCheckbox({name:'twelve',label:'Use 12-hour clock',value:false}).addText({name:'format',label:'Format',value:'yyyy/MM/dd hh:mm:ss'}).addText({name:'formatInfo',label:'Format Placeholders',value:' - Year
yy: 2-digit year
yyyy: 4-digit year

 - Month
M: numeric month (e.g. 3)
MM: 2-digit month (e.g. 03)

 - Day
d: numeric day (e.g. 5)
dd: 2-digit day (e.g. 05)

 - Weekday
W: Weekday placeholder

 - Hour
h: numeric hour (e.g. 4)
hh: 2-digit hour (e.g. 04)

 - Minute
m: numeric minute (e.g. 7)
mm: 2-digit minute (e.g. 07)

 - Second
s: numeric second (e.g. 1)
ss: 2-digit second (e.g. 01)

 - Millisecond
S: Millisecond placeholder (Max up to 3 digits)

 - AMPM
a: AMPM placeholder
※ Note ※
You must enable the 'Use 12-hour clock' to use this placeholder'}).finish();export function update(value){const now=new Date();let nowObject={year:"",month:"",day:"",week:"",hour:"",minute:"",second:"",millisecond:"",ampm:""};const setting={lang:scriptProperties.language,weektype:scriptProperties.week,twelve:scriptProperties.twelve,year:scriptProperties.format.match(/y+/)?scriptProperties.format.match(/y+/)[0]:"",month:scriptProperties.format.match(/M+/)?scriptProperties.format.match(/M+/)[0]:"",day:scriptProperties.format.match(/d+/)?scriptProperties.format.match(/d+/)[0]:"",week:scriptProperties.format.match(/W+/)?scriptProperties.format.match(/W+/)[0]:"",hour:scriptProperties.format.match(/h+/)?scriptProperties.format.match(/h+/)[0]:"",minute:scriptProperties.format.match(/m+/)?scriptProperties.format.match(/m+/)[0]:"",second:scriptProperties.format.match(/s+/)?scriptProperties.format.match(/s+/)[0]:"",millisecond:scriptProperties.format.match(/S+/)?scriptProperties.format.match(/S+/)[0]:"",ampm:scriptProperties.format.match(/a+/)?scriptProperties.format.match(/a+/)[0]:""};const weekday={"en-US":{narrow:["S","M","T","W","T","F","S"],short:["Sun","Mon","Tue","Wed","Thu","Fri","Sat"],long:["Sunday","Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Saturday"]},"zh-TW":{narrow:["日","一","二","三","四","五","六"],short:["週日","週一","週二","週三","週四","週五","週六"],long:["星期日","星期一","星期二","星期三","星期四","星期五","星期六"]},"ja-JP":{long:["日","月","火","水","木","金","土"],short:["日曜","月曜","火曜","水曜","木曜","金曜","土曜"],long:["日曜日","月曜日","火曜日","水曜日","木曜日","金曜日","土曜日"]}};const ampmlang={"en-US":["AM","PM"],"zh-TW":["上午","下午"],"ja-JP":["午前","午後"]};if(setting.year.length==2)nowObject.year=now.getFullYear().toString().slice(2);else if(setting.year.length==4)nowObject.year=now.getFullYear().toString();else nowObject.year=setting.year;if(setting.month.length==1)nowObject.month=(now.getMonth()+1).toString();else if(setting.month.length==2)nowObject.month=(now.getMonth()+1).toString().length==1?"0" +(now.getMonth()+1).toString():(now.getMonth()+1).toString();else nowObject.month=setting.month;if(setting.day.length==1)nowObject.day=now.getDate();else if(setting.day.length==2)nowObject.day=now.getDate().toString().length==1?"0"+now.getDate().toString():now.getDate().toString();else nowObject.day=setting.day;if(setting.week.length==1)nowObject.week=weekday[setting.lang][setting.weektype][now.getDay()];else nowObject.week=setting.week;if(setting.twelve){if(setting.hour.length==1)nowObject.hour=now.getHours()>12?(now.getHours()-12).toString():now.getHours().toString();else if(setting.hour.length==2)nowObject.hour=(now.getHours()>12?(now.getHours()-12).toString():now.getHours().toString()).length==1?"0"+now.getHours()>12?(now.getHours()-12).toString():now.getHours().toString():now.getHours()>12?(now.getHours()-12).toString():now.getHours().toString();else nowObject.hour=setting.hour;}else{if(setting.hour.length==1)nowObject.hour=now.getHours();else if(setting.hour.length==2)nowObject.hour=now.getHours().toString().length==1?"0"+now.getHours().toString():now.getHours().toString();else nowObject.hour=setting.hour;}if(setting.minute.length==1)nowObject.minute=now.getMinutes();else if(setting.minute.length==2)nowObject.minute=now.getMinutes().toString().length==1?"0"+now.getMinutes().toString():now.getMinutes().toString();else nowObject.minute=setting.minute;if(setting.second.length==1)nowObject.second=now.getSeconds();else if(setting.second.length==2)nowObject.second=now.getSeconds().toString().length==1?"0"+now.getSeconds().toString():now.getSeconds().toString();else nowObject.second=setting.second;if(setting.millisecond.length==1)nowObject.millisecond=now.getMilliseconds().toString().slice(0,1);else if(setting.millisecond.length==2)nowObject.millisecond=now.getMilliseconds().toString().slice(0,2);else if(setting.millisecond.length==3)nowObject.millisecond=now.getMilliseconds().toString();else nowObject.millisecond=setting.millisecond;if(setting.ampm.length==1 && setting.twelve){nowObject.ampm=now.getHours()>12?ampmlang[setting.lang][1]:ampmlang[setting.lang][0];}else nowObject.ampm=setting.ampm;let output=scriptProperties.format;output=output.replace(/y+/,nowObject.year);output=output.replace(/M+/,nowObject.month);output=output.replace(/d+/,nowObject.day);output=output.replace(/h+/,nowObject.hour);output=output.replace(/m+/,nowObject.minute);output=output.replace(/s+/,nowObject.second);output=output.replace(/S+/,nowObject.millisecond);output=output.replace(/a+/,nowObject.ampm);output=output.replace(/W+/,nowObject.week);return output;}
